1
00:01:30,320 --> 00:01:31,600
Otherwise, you being you,

2
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:33,080
who would ever take you in?

3
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:35,320
Fine.

4
00:01:36,039 --> 00:01:37,080
- It's no big deal.
- Wait.

5
00:01:38,080 --> 00:01:39,039
My Lord,

6
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:40,759
do you plan to use the Marquis's power

7
00:01:40,960 --> 00:01:42,320
to bear the Liu family down?

8
00:01:44,240 --> 00:01:45,400
Since I gave you my word,

9
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:46,640
I will see it through.

10
00:01:46,960 --> 00:01:47,680
You don't get to

11
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:48,840
tell me how to do my job.

12
00:01:49,880 --> 00:01:51,120
What if I have a way

13
00:01:51,280 --> 00:01:52,920
to keep you out of this?

14
00:01:54,240 --> 00:01:55,080
What is it?

15
00:01:55,800 --> 00:01:57,160
This is my foster-charm.

16
00:01:57,640 --> 00:01:58,440
Since I was a child,

17
00:01:58,440 --> 00:02:00,160
I've been under Priest Qingxu's protection.

18
00:02:00,840 --> 00:02:02,520
One word from this man

19
00:02:02,520 --> 00:02:03,200
and my Father

20
00:02:03,200 --> 00:02:04,760
sent me away to Tongzhou.

21
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:05,920
I was still in swaddling clothes.

22
00:02:06,440 --> 00:02:08,520
If he is willing to step in,

23
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:10,280
Father is ours.

24
00:02:11,440 --> 00:02:12,960
However, Xuanmiao Temple

25
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:13,960
is a royal sanctuary.

26
00:02:14,200 --> 00:02:15,120
Without your help

27
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:17,360
I wouldn't be able to access.

28
00:02:18,360 --> 00:02:19,560
In that case, you should

29
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:21,280
hate this Priest Qingxu

30
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,120
to your very core.

31
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,560
Why turn to him?

32
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:29,079
A liar is detestable, no doubt about that,

33
00:02:29,600 --> 00:02:30,840
but being gullible

34
00:02:31,079 --> 00:02:32,200
is no less a crime.

35
00:02:32,920 --> 00:02:34,880
That priest is after none other than money.

36
00:02:35,360 --> 00:02:36,400
And money I have plenty of.

37
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:38,079
If Father can use him,

38
00:02:38,320 --> 00:02:39,120
so can I.

39
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:44,320
Wait.

40
00:02:45,040 --> 00:02:46,040
What happened to your hand?

41
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:49,720
What's all this about?

42
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:52,040
W... Why do you care?

43
00:02:52,920 --> 00:02:53,880
Hands off me.

44
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:55,240
You didn't

45
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:56,400
get yourself beaten, did you?

46
00:02:56,880 --> 00:02:57,800
By whom?

47
00:03:00,040 --> 00:03:01,200
Who else could it be?

48
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:02,640
Whoever you've been

49
00:03:02,640 --> 00:03:03,680
so desperate to please.

50
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:06,160
Mr. Chen?

51
00:03:07,880 --> 00:03:08,760
How...

52
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,920
Stop being a busybody.

53
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,120
I'm leaving.

54
00:03:16,600 --> 00:03:17,520
When I have news,

55
00:03:18,079 --> 00:03:19,360
I'll send Li Xianhuai here.

56
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:35,960
Foster-charm, seriously?

57
00:03:36,480 --> 00:03:37,840
Are you smart or reckless?

58
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:46,760
Ye Xian,

59
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:52,000
are you here to see Jinzhao?

60
00:03:53,760 --> 00:03:54,920
I heard you were

61
00:03:55,000 --> 00:03:56,600
just chosen as the Prince's study partner.

62
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:58,400
How do you have time to be out?

63
00:04:00,520 --> 00:04:01,520
I'm attending the palace,

64
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:02,680
not doing time.

65
00:04:28,720 --> 00:04:30,640
You seem troubled, Miss.

66
00:04:31,200 --> 00:04:31,760
Tell me,

67
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:33,320
do you think Ye Xian

68
00:04:33,320 --> 00:04:34,440
might have feelings

69
00:04:34,520 --> 00:04:35,280
for Jinzhao?

70
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:37,560
I'm not sure I follow.

71
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,600
He was supposed to be

72
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,240
in the palace.

73
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:41,480
Yet for Jinzhao's sake,

74
00:04:41,800 --> 00:04:42,600
he cared to

75
00:04:42,760 --> 00:04:43,840
show up himself.

76
00:04:44,880 --> 00:04:45,240
I mean,

77
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:46,360
what is he trying to imply?

78
00:04:46,960 --> 00:04:48,040
Miss Jinzhao has only been back

79
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,200
for a month and a half.

80
00:04:51,320 --> 00:04:53,520
I doubt his Lordship

81
00:04:53,640 --> 00:04:54,960
has much of a history with her.

82
00:04:55,220 --> 00:04:57,060
It's only been a month,

83
00:04:57,140 --> 00:04:58,740
yet how many times have they met?

84
00:04:59,480 --> 00:05:00,280
They met at Jinzhao's

85
00:05:00,280 --> 00:05:01,160
coming-of-age ceremony.

86
00:05:01,440 --> 00:05:02,800
They shared a carriage home.

87
00:05:03,400 --> 00:05:04,920
Then again at the Lin family banquet,

88
00:05:05,200 --> 00:05:05,800
and now today.

89
00:05:06,020 --> 00:05:07,160
What are the odds?

90
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:10,880
I only get to see him

91
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,320
once a year when we return

92
00:05:12,320 --> 00:05:13,920
to the ancestral home for New Year's.

93
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:25,920
This time,

94
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:28,000
Xuanqing ranked first in the exam,

95
00:05:28,000 --> 00:05:29,520
following in your footsteps.

96
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:32,360
Come to think of his biological father,

97
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:34,280
this is going to be tricky.

98
00:05:34,640 --> 00:05:36,480
Xuanqing is his own man,

99
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:38,040
not his father's.

100
00:05:42,520 --> 00:05:43,120
Sir,

101
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,840
the Ji family's here with gifts.

102
00:05:47,560 --> 00:05:48,720
The Mid-Autumn has passed.

103
00:05:49,240 --> 00:05:50,440
What kind of gifts?

104
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:01,760
Speaking of opulence.

105
00:06:03,440 --> 00:06:05,200
This set of jade paperweights alone

106
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:06,840
must be worth a fortune.

107
00:06:07,120 --> 00:06:08,400
She's still uneasy.

108
00:06:08,960 --> 00:06:09,560
Oh?

109
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:12,400
Is there a message in these?

110
00:06:13,440 --> 00:06:15,000
The driver we planted at the Gu Manor

111
00:06:15,000 --> 00:06:16,000
has been withdrawn,

112
00:06:16,480 --> 00:06:17,600
but she's still wary.

113
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:18,960
So you see,

114
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:20,440
she sent this

115
00:06:20,680 --> 00:06:22,200
jade carving of a carriage

116
00:06:22,600 --> 00:06:23,600
to test the waters.

117
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:25,560
And as for

118
00:06:25,960 --> 00:06:27,000
these jade paperweights...

119
00:06:27,360 --> 00:06:29,360
Two turquoise, two opalescent.

120
00:06:30,020 --> 00:06:31,540
It's her way of saying she's innocent.

121
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:33,240
And these motifs—

122
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:35,800
plum, orchid, bamboo, and chrysanthemum.

123
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:37,840
Symbols of virtue.

124
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:40,560
She hopes I'll act with integrity.

125
00:06:40,840 --> 00:06:42,080
It's also a thank-you

126
00:06:42,320 --> 00:06:43,760
for helping Ye Xian leave the palace.

127
00:06:43,760 --> 00:06:45,680
Miss Gu...

128
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:48,440
She's quite the clever one.

129
00:06:48,840 --> 00:06:50,010
She's just a young girl after all,

130
00:06:50,950 --> 00:06:52,420
living in constant fear.

131
00:06:54,320 --> 00:06:55,760
It truly breaks one's heart.

132
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:08,720
Greetings, my Lord.

133
00:07:09,280 --> 00:07:10,400
Priest Qingxu?

134
00:07:11,800 --> 00:07:12,960
I assume you recognize

135
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:14,360
this foster-charm?

136
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:16,360
This is...

137
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:24,320
Today, Priest Qingxu came to

138
00:07:24,840 --> 00:07:26,520
Yongding Manor for a ritual

139
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:28,400
and specifically asked to see me.

140
00:07:29,400 --> 00:07:30,640
So, I had him look over

141
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:32,840
Jinzhao's and Liu Xiancheng's birth charts

142
00:07:33,080 --> 00:07:34,520
and asked him for his insight.

143
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:36,920
And?

144
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:42,560
Jinzhao's chart is fine now.

145
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:45,240
He once said she'd hinder my career.

146
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:48,120
Now that she's of age,

147
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:49,600
that particular curse

148
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,960
seems to have lifted.

149
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:56,400
However, Liu Xiancheng's chart

150
00:07:56,400 --> 00:07:57,520
is quite unfavorable.

151
00:07:58,200 --> 00:07:59,159
It suggests...

152
00:07:59,960 --> 00:08:02,080
he brings misfortune to his kin.

153
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:03,560
While "kin" doesn't

154
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,720
include his in-laws,

155
00:08:06,440 --> 00:08:07,400
his destiny is simply

156
00:08:07,960 --> 00:08:09,360
too harsh.

157
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:11,280
In my opinion,

158
00:08:11,840 --> 00:08:13,440
we should probably

159
00:08:15,600 --> 00:08:16,520
ditch the marriage.

160
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:18,400
Well,

161
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:19,720
fortunately,

162
00:08:20,280 --> 00:08:21,360
Jinzhao's betrothal card

163
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,600
hasn't been delivered yet.

164
00:08:23,480 --> 00:08:25,120
If we were to back out later,

165
00:08:25,320 --> 00:08:27,160
it would ruin Jinzhao's reputation.

166
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:29,680
We can't tell them the truth.

167
00:08:31,360 --> 00:08:32,880
Let them know that

168
00:08:33,320 --> 00:08:34,679
Jinzhao's Grandmother

169
00:08:34,679 --> 00:08:36,120
can't bear to see her wed so soon.

170
00:08:36,400 --> 00:08:37,240
That way,

171
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:40,200
we give the Lius an explanation

172
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:43,000
while protecting Jinzhao's name.

173
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:45,120
All of a sudden,

174
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,520
my reputation matters, Father?

175
00:08:47,680 --> 00:08:48,640
What a pity.

176
00:08:50,240 --> 00:08:51,280
My reputation...

177
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:52,960
is likely beyond saving.

178
00:08:53,240 --> 00:08:54,240
In that case,

179
00:08:54,640 --> 00:08:55,920
strive to mend your ways.

180
00:08:56,880 --> 00:08:58,200
It's not up to me.

181
00:08:58,480 --> 00:09:00,200
There's someone bribing their ways,

182
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:02,320
hell-bent on smearing mud on me.

183
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:04,640
Wait...

184
00:09:04,880 --> 00:09:05,760
What?

185
00:09:15,160 --> 00:09:16,440
Song Miaohua!

186
00:09:17,600 --> 00:09:19,920
How ungrateful of you!

187
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:21,280
Ma'am!

188
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:22,760
I've never broken

189
00:09:22,760 --> 00:09:23,800
any of this to her.

190
00:09:24,480 --> 00:09:25,200
Ma'am,

191
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:27,320
I warned her long ago

192
00:09:27,520 --> 00:09:30,640
the Liu family's son is a lecher.

193
00:09:30,920 --> 00:09:31,560
He's got

194
00:09:31,560 --> 00:09:32,720
bed-warming maids

195
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:34,320
and a secret mistress

196
00:09:34,320 --> 00:09:35,480
for over a year now.

197
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:36,240
He's...

198
00:09:37,200 --> 00:09:38,080
What?

199
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:39,120
He's got...

200
00:09:41,920 --> 00:09:44,440
I've been meaning to report this to you, Ma'am.

201
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:45,240
But...

202
00:09:45,520 --> 00:09:47,320
It was Nanny Zhou.

203
00:09:47,640 --> 00:09:48,280
She...

204
00:09:48,280 --> 00:09:49,640
She blocked me at every turn.

205
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:52,760
She said master’s countenanced on this matter,

206
00:09:52,880 --> 00:09:54,800
and it wasn't for me to poke my nose into it.

207
00:09:55,760 --> 00:09:56,960
Absolutely outrageous!

208
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:58,520
Every word I've said is true.

209
00:09:58,920 --> 00:10:00,160
If I've told a single lie,

210
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:01,480
may my tongue rot away,

211
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:02,720
and let me die a wretched death.

212
00:10:03,880 --> 00:10:04,720
Song Miaohua!

213
00:10:05,480 --> 00:10:06,640
The nerve of you!

214
00:10:07,960 --> 00:10:10,000
How dare you keep me in the dark about this?

215
00:10:11,720 --> 00:10:12,600
A family like that...

216
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:14,480
If Jinzhao were to marry into that house,

217
00:10:14,920 --> 00:10:16,480
what kind of future would she have?

218
00:10:17,920 --> 00:10:18,760
Nanny Zhao!

219
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:20,240
I want the two of them

220
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:21,680
out of my sight.

221
00:10:21,760 --> 00:10:22,960
Fifty strokes each.

222
00:10:23,120 --> 00:10:24,040
Pack them off to the country.

223
00:10:24,160 --> 00:10:25,520
Make them gone for good.

224
00:10:25,920 --> 00:10:26,560
Yes, Ma'am.

225
00:10:26,560 --> 00:10:27,240
Ma'am, please... I...

226
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:28,360
Ma'am!

227
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,160
Master!

228
00:10:30,520 --> 00:10:31,960
Say something, I beg you!

229
00:10:32,520 --> 00:10:33,240
Well...

230
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:35,640
You have truly

231
00:10:35,760 --> 00:10:36,920
crossed the line here.

232
00:10:37,560 --> 00:10:38,760
You are not getting away with this.

233
00:10:39,120 --> 00:10:40,000
Again...

234
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:41,600
Taking her away from Lan seems too much.

235
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:43,080
She doesn't deserve

236
00:10:43,080 --> 00:10:43,880
banishment.

237
00:10:44,040 --> 00:10:45,040
But the strokes are no goner.

238
00:10:45,280 --> 00:10:46,960
Twenty each.

239
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:48,000
It's not fair!

240
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:49,800
You told me to

241
00:10:49,800 --> 00:10:51,320
to match her with that Liu boy!

242
00:10:51,520 --> 00:10:52,560
You knew every bit of

243
00:10:52,560 --> 00:10:53,520
the filth about his family.

244
00:10:54,440 --> 00:10:55,360
Nanny Zhou and I

245
00:10:55,800 --> 00:10:57,040
were only doing your bidding.

246
00:10:57,160 --> 00:10:58,320
Why should I take the fall?

247
00:10:58,440 --> 00:10:59,680
What are you talking about?

248
00:11:00,560 --> 00:11:01,800
How dare you pin this on me?

249
00:11:02,320 --> 00:11:03,480
I told you to arrange a match,

250
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:05,120
not to make a laughingstock of us!

251
00:11:05,400 --> 00:11:06,280
But... I...

252
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:07,320
My Lady!

253
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:08,600
Please, don't.

254
00:11:09,320 --> 00:11:10,200
Master, Ma'am,

255
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:11,160
this is all my doing.

256
00:11:11,320 --> 00:11:12,320
She was completely

257
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:13,840
in the dark.

258
00:11:13,840 --> 00:11:14,720
Nanny Zhou,

259
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:16,080
nice try covering

260
00:11:16,080 --> 00:11:16,800
for your lady.

261
00:11:17,280 --> 00:11:18,320
But I don't think you'd

262
00:11:18,320 --> 00:11:19,200
have taken the risk

263
00:11:19,680 --> 00:11:20,600
if she hadn't nodded.

264
00:11:21,040 --> 00:11:21,920
That's not true!

265
00:11:22,280 --> 00:11:23,080
I've been framed!

266
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:23,560
I...

267
00:11:25,760 --> 00:11:26,560
Gu Dezhao!

268
00:11:26,920 --> 00:11:27,640
When you asked me

269
00:11:27,640 --> 00:11:28,840
to find a match for Jinzhao,

270
00:11:28,840 --> 00:11:30,200
I knew it was a bad idea.

271
00:11:30,520 --> 00:11:31,440
I knew this would be

272
00:11:31,440 --> 00:11:32,600
a thankless task,

273
00:11:32,800 --> 00:11:34,080
but you insisted I handle it.

274
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:35,840
I was raised as a

275
00:11:35,840 --> 00:11:37,600
proper lady myself.

276
00:11:38,400 --> 00:11:39,800
What do I know of such schemes?

277
00:11:40,040 --> 00:11:40,920
If I were that cunning

278
00:11:40,920 --> 00:11:42,440
about the ways of the world,

279
00:11:42,560 --> 00:11:43,400
would I ever have

280
00:11:43,400 --> 00:11:44,680
defied my parents' wishes,

281
00:11:45,040 --> 00:11:46,720
refused every penny of dowry,

282
00:11:46,720 --> 00:11:48,040
and fought to be your concubine?

283
00:11:48,400 --> 00:11:48,840
You...

284
00:11:49,160 --> 00:11:50,280
No, I mean...

285
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:51,400
I...

286
00:11:51,400 --> 00:11:52,360
Damn you!

287
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:54,680
Ungrateful scum!

288
00:11:55,120 --> 00:11:56,760
I'm the pearl on my family's crown!

289
00:11:57,040 --> 00:11:58,400
Solely for this marriage,

290
00:11:58,600 --> 00:12:00,440
my parents disowned me.

291
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:02,640
It's been a decade and they never paid me a visit.

292
00:12:02,880 --> 00:12:04,480
I've born your children,

293
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:06,080
run your household.

294
00:12:06,400 --> 00:12:08,880
And yet, while you all dine in comfort,

295
00:12:08,880 --> 00:12:10,560
I must stand and wait on you.

296
00:12:11,010 --> 00:12:12,480
And now, you want to beat me?

297
00:12:12,520 --> 00:12:13,400
Look at me!

298
00:12:13,400 --> 00:12:14,480
Alright, alright.

299
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:15,840
- I know you've had it hard.
- Mother!

300
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:18,800
Lan!

301
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:21,320
Don't you dare bully my mother!

302
00:12:22,560 --> 00:12:23,280
You...

303
00:12:23,760 --> 00:12:24,440
And you!

304
00:12:26,920 --> 00:12:27,520
Ma'am!

305
00:12:28,720 --> 00:12:29,480
Ma'am! Ma'am!

306
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:31,720
Quickly, someone!

307
00:12:31,920 --> 00:12:32,480
Ma'am!

308
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:34,000
Get her back to her room!

309
00:12:34,280 --> 00:12:35,360
Go and fetch the physician!

310
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:36,240
Hurry!

311
00:12:36,400 --> 00:12:37,480
Careful, now. Move gently.

312
00:12:46,040 --> 00:12:46,920
Miaohua...

313
00:12:47,880 --> 00:12:48,400
Woe is me!

314
00:12:48,400 --> 00:12:49,240
Don't cry. It's alright.

315
00:12:49,320 --> 00:12:49,880
There, there...

316
00:12:50,080 --> 00:12:50,640
Everything is fine.

317
00:12:52,000 --> 00:12:54,120
I know it's been unfair for you.

318
00:12:54,600 --> 00:12:55,640
Stop crying now.

319
00:12:56,880 --> 00:12:58,240
Did you hear the Master?

320
00:12:58,840 --> 00:12:59,480
Drag her out!

321
00:12:59,760 --> 00:13:00,800
Make sure she feels every stroke!

322
00:13:02,520 --> 00:13:03,120
- Dezhao!
- Father!

323
00:13:03,520 --> 00:13:03,920
Master!

324
00:13:03,920 --> 00:13:04,640
Take her away!

325
00:13:05,000 --> 00:13:05,880
Don't you touch my mother!

326
00:13:06,360 --> 00:13:07,240
Get your hands off her!

327
00:13:07,480 --> 00:13:08,320
Hands off her!

328
00:13:08,680 --> 00:13:09,560
Let her go!

329
00:13:09,600 --> 00:13:10,320
Move!

330
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:12,120
Get a move on!

331
00:13:54,560 --> 00:13:55,720
At a time like this,

332
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:56,920
how can you even have an appetite?

333
00:13:57,640 --> 00:13:58,960
Why shouldn't I?

334
00:13:59,760 --> 00:14:01,000
It wasn't me who caused the mess.

335
00:14:01,480 --> 00:14:02,560
How come you

336
00:14:02,560 --> 00:14:03,720
got caught red-handed?

337
00:14:04,320 --> 00:14:04,960
Nanny Zhou

338
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:06,240
was too desperate for revenge.

339
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:07,480
She thought the marriage

340
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:08,360
was set in stone,

341
00:14:08,640 --> 00:14:10,280
so she had the matchmaker stir the pot.

342
00:14:10,680 --> 00:14:12,040
Who knew it would all blow up?

343
00:14:12,320 --> 00:14:13,760
Of course it fell through.

344
00:14:14,040 --> 00:14:15,480
You've all misjudged Jinzhao.

345
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:17,040
She has her sights set much higher.

346
00:14:17,320 --> 00:14:18,560
She'd never settle for the likes of him.

347
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:19,800
What do you mean?

348
00:14:20,600 --> 00:14:21,680
My Lady...

349
00:14:22,720 --> 00:14:23,320
What's up?

350
00:14:23,880 --> 00:14:25,560
Master is staying with Ma'am tonight.

351
00:14:25,920 --> 00:14:27,720
The lights are already out.

352
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:30,480
Fine, let him stay away.

353
00:14:30,480 --> 00:14:31,160
I'm sick of him anyway.

354
00:14:32,960 --> 00:14:34,640
But what about Nanny Zhou?

355
00:14:35,080 --> 00:14:36,200
It's getting chilly outside,

356
00:14:36,320 --> 00:14:37,320
and that woodshed is freezing.

357
00:14:37,960 --> 00:14:39,600
She'll catch her death in there.

358
00:14:41,760 --> 00:14:42,720
My people are under watch.

359
00:14:43,120 --> 00:14:44,000
Take Ziling with you

360
00:14:44,280 --> 00:14:45,360
and bring her a blanket.

361
00:14:45,920 --> 00:14:46,440
Yes.

362
00:14:46,920 --> 00:14:47,520
I'm not going.

363
00:14:47,800 --> 00:14:48,600
You wild girl!

364
00:14:49,360 --> 00:14:49,920
Any idea

365
00:14:49,920 --> 00:14:51,080
how many times she used to

366
00:14:51,080 --> 00:14:52,000
clean up after you?

367
00:14:52,520 --> 00:14:53,800
Show some gratitude.

368
00:14:54,400 --> 00:14:55,160
So you won't go?

369
00:14:55,640 --> 00:14:56,080
Fine.

370
00:14:56,440 --> 00:14:57,720
I'll just force my way out then.

371
00:15:00,560 --> 00:15:01,840
Don't venture!

372
00:15:02,400 --> 00:15:03,400
It took everything

373
00:15:03,400 --> 00:15:04,400
to placate Father.

374
00:15:04,560 --> 00:15:05,120
Don't give him

375
00:15:05,120 --> 00:15:06,320
another excuse to throw you out.

376
00:15:41,840 --> 00:15:43,610
Bless you, Lan.

377
00:15:44,840 --> 00:15:46,480
How is my lady?

378
00:15:46,720 --> 00:15:47,880
She's miserable.

379
00:15:48,400 --> 00:15:49,560
Your mess has ruined her.

380
00:15:50,040 --> 00:15:51,680
I have failed her.

381
00:15:53,920 --> 00:15:55,760
Did Master go to see her?

382
00:15:56,200 --> 00:15:57,160
Hardly.

383
00:15:57,560 --> 00:15:58,800
Ma'am fainted.

384
00:15:58,960 --> 00:15:59,560
Where else

385
00:15:59,560 --> 00:16:00,960
is Father going to be?

386
00:16:01,360 --> 00:16:02,960
So, he's in Ma'am's room...

387
00:16:04,440 --> 00:16:04,960
Good.

388
00:16:05,760 --> 00:16:06,640
Very good.

389
00:16:09,120 --> 00:16:10,080
Lan,

390
00:16:10,560 --> 00:16:11,520
can I ask you to

391
00:16:11,960 --> 00:16:13,560
take a message to my lady?

392
00:16:14,410 --> 00:16:15,650
What stupidity this time?

393
00:16:16,210 --> 00:16:17,190
It's not stupid.

394
00:16:17,870 --> 00:16:18,970
It's to help her

395
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:20,180
win back the favor.

396
00:16:35,440 --> 00:16:36,640
My Lady, the Master's orders were

397
00:16:36,640 --> 00:16:38,040
for you to stay in your quarters.

398
00:16:38,480 --> 00:16:39,680
What brings you here?

399
00:16:40,320 --> 00:16:42,240
I've come to beg the Ma'am's forgiveness.

400
00:16:47,360 --> 00:16:48,600
Here are the household tallies

401
00:16:48,800 --> 00:16:50,040
and the keys to the storehouse.

402
00:16:50,640 --> 00:16:52,320
Now that I am overwhelmed by shame.

403
00:16:53,360 --> 00:16:55,160
I'm not in the position to run this household.

404
00:16:55,680 --> 00:16:56,800
So I am here to return

405
00:16:56,800 --> 00:16:58,040
all of this to Ma'am.

406
00:17:03,080 --> 00:17:04,680
I await Ma'am's punishment.

407
00:17:06,680 --> 00:17:07,280
Well...

408
00:17:15,040 --> 00:17:16,480
I beg Ma'am for mercy.

409
00:17:44,080 --> 00:17:45,200
Song Miaohua and Nanny Zhou

410
00:17:45,200 --> 00:17:46,560
paid off the matchmaker.

411
00:17:47,040 --> 00:17:47,760
This wasn't just aimed at

412
00:17:47,760 --> 00:17:49,160
ruining my reputation for life,

413
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:50,640
but at dragging our

414
00:17:50,640 --> 00:17:51,680
family through the mud.

415
00:17:52,960 --> 00:17:53,600
How can you

416
00:17:53,840 --> 00:17:54,520
tolerate them?

417
00:17:55,360 --> 00:17:56,480
How would I

418
00:17:57,040 --> 00:17:58,240
not see it all?

419
00:17:59,120 --> 00:18:00,840
But I know your father.

420
00:18:01,480 --> 00:18:02,360
If I were to insist on

421
00:18:02,360 --> 00:18:03,760
driving out Nanny Zhou

422
00:18:04,520 --> 00:18:05,800
and punishing Song Miaohua,

423
00:18:06,320 --> 00:18:07,000
I'm afraid

424
00:18:07,000 --> 00:18:08,440
that the marital bond

425
00:18:08,600 --> 00:18:09,880
would end then and there.

426
00:18:10,640 --> 00:18:11,520
But why must you and I

427
00:18:11,880 --> 00:18:13,200
swallow the bitter pill?

428
00:18:14,240 --> 00:18:15,240
That makes no sense.

429
00:18:16,120 --> 00:18:16,960
You're still too young

430
00:18:17,120 --> 00:18:17,800
to understand.

431
00:18:18,120 --> 00:18:19,520
Between a husband and wife,

432
00:18:19,720 --> 00:18:21,080
reason was never meant to rule.

433
00:18:22,040 --> 00:18:22,800
It's only...

434
00:18:24,440 --> 00:18:25,680
I've made you suffer, sweetheart.

435
00:18:42,360 --> 00:18:43,320
Sir. Sir.

436
00:18:47,720 --> 00:18:48,600
Sir.

437
00:18:51,280 --> 00:18:52,560
Then we hire an opera troupe

438
00:18:53,040 --> 00:18:54,440
and have them perform

439
00:18:54,920 --> 00:18:56,560
for three days straight.

440
00:18:57,440 --> 00:18:58,320
Sir has arrived.

441
00:19:04,760 --> 00:19:05,400
- Uncle.
- Brother.

442
00:19:05,680 --> 00:19:06,360
You're all here.

443
00:19:09,040 --> 00:19:09,520
Mother.

444
00:19:09,920 --> 00:19:10,840
Here you are.

445
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:11,680
Have a seat.

446
00:19:12,640 --> 00:19:13,120
Alright.

447
00:19:19,760 --> 00:19:21,120
We were just discussing

448
00:19:21,760 --> 00:19:23,400
holding a banquet for Xuanqing

449
00:19:23,400 --> 00:19:24,320
and your brother.

450
00:19:26,080 --> 00:19:26,600
Mother,

451
00:19:27,000 --> 00:19:27,680
I was just about

452
00:19:28,280 --> 00:19:30,160
to discuss this matter with you.

453
00:19:32,040 --> 00:19:32,800
Right now,

454
00:19:33,320 --> 00:19:34,880
there's a storm looming large at court.

455
00:19:35,320 --> 00:19:36,560
We should keep a low profile.

456
00:19:37,120 --> 00:19:37,720
Better

457
00:19:38,080 --> 00:19:39,440
forget about the banquet for now.

458
00:19:41,840 --> 00:19:42,480
Why?

459
00:19:42,960 --> 00:19:43,440
It's only

460
00:19:43,440 --> 00:19:44,680
a little gathering.

461
00:19:45,040 --> 00:19:45,880
Since when was that illegal?

462
00:19:46,920 --> 00:19:47,720
Exactly.

463
00:19:48,040 --> 00:19:50,120
A glory like this deserves a feast.

464
00:19:50,760 --> 00:19:51,680
Think about it, Brother.

465
00:19:52,080 --> 00:19:53,240
If my passing the exam isn't

466
00:19:53,560 --> 00:19:54,280
reason to celebrate,

467
00:19:54,360 --> 00:19:55,480
Xuanqing's made it to the top!

468
00:19:58,160 --> 00:19:58,800
Grandmother.

469
00:20:00,120 --> 00:20:01,120
Uncle, your kindness

470
00:20:01,120 --> 00:20:02,240
fills me with gratitude.

471
00:20:03,520 --> 00:20:04,200
I'm sure Uncle

472
00:20:04,200 --> 00:20:05,200
has his reasons.

473
00:20:05,920 --> 00:20:06,440
Uncle is

474
00:20:06,440 --> 00:20:07,960
single-handedly pushing the tax reforms.

475
00:20:08,280 --> 00:20:09,760
He's at the center of the storm.

476
00:20:10,400 --> 00:20:11,040
He must be

477
00:20:11,040 --> 00:20:12,400
under countless pairs of eyes.

478
00:20:12,640 --> 00:20:13,800
Holding a feast now

479
00:20:14,200 --> 00:20:15,520
invites attacks from his enemies.

480
00:20:16,440 --> 00:20:17,200
That would likely

481
00:20:18,040 --> 00:20:19,760
reflect poorly on the entire family.

482
00:20:23,360 --> 00:20:25,080
Turns out I am the

483
00:20:25,080 --> 00:20:26,360
unreasonable one all along.

484
00:20:27,040 --> 00:20:28,000
It's not like that, Mother.

485
00:20:30,200 --> 00:20:31,320
If that was all

486
00:20:31,520 --> 00:20:32,600
you've got to say to me,

487
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:36,280
you can excuse yourself.

488
00:21:03,720 --> 00:21:05,240
So accustomed now is Yanyun to power.

489
00:21:05,320 --> 00:21:06,200
Nobody under this roof

490
00:21:06,200 --> 00:21:07,280
could keep him in check now.

491
00:21:07,800 --> 00:21:08,400
Mother,

492
00:21:08,880 --> 00:21:10,320
you are the head of this household.

493
00:21:10,520 --> 00:21:11,400
Surely you have a say

494
00:21:11,400 --> 00:21:12,720
on a little banquet?

495
00:21:13,160 --> 00:21:13,800
I don't care.

496
00:21:14,400 --> 00:21:15,040
I'm throwing it,

497
00:21:15,040 --> 00:21:15,800
no matter what.

498
00:21:16,040 --> 00:21:16,480
But...

499
00:21:16,480 --> 00:21:17,240
But what?

500
00:21:17,720 --> 00:21:18,280
Xuanqing.

501
00:21:18,840 --> 00:21:19,720
Let's not forget,

502
00:21:20,480 --> 00:21:21,920
even though your surname is Chen,

503
00:21:22,480 --> 00:21:23,320
you're in no position

504
00:21:23,320 --> 00:21:24,520
to speak your mind.

505
00:21:25,120 --> 00:21:25,920
Watch your mouth.

506
00:21:26,840 --> 00:21:29,120
Xuanqing is your little brother's heir.

507
00:21:32,040 --> 00:21:33,240
In my opinion,

508
00:21:33,680 --> 00:21:35,640
we needn't make it a lavish affair.

509
00:21:36,280 --> 00:21:38,800
Let's just invite some close family and friends over.

510
00:21:39,480 --> 00:21:40,520
We won't even break

511
00:21:40,640 --> 00:21:42,640
that it is a celebration at all.

512
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:43,800
Rather,

513
00:21:44,040 --> 00:21:46,440
the chrysanthemums in the courtyard are in full bloom

514
00:21:46,960 --> 00:21:49,000
and we're inviting everyone to come admire them.

515
00:21:49,800 --> 00:21:50,920
I don't expect Yanyun

516
00:21:51,560 --> 00:21:53,000
will further object.

517
00:21:56,560 --> 00:21:57,600
We'll do as Mother wishes.

518
00:21:59,120 --> 00:21:59,560
You.

519
00:22:00,160 --> 00:22:01,320
Deliver those invites

520
00:22:01,320 --> 00:22:02,160
without delay.

521
00:22:02,720 --> 00:22:03,800
Make sure every single one

522
00:22:03,800 --> 00:22:05,000
of those former classmates of mine

523
00:22:05,560 --> 00:22:06,720
who didn't pass the exam.

524
00:22:08,080 --> 00:22:08,680
Sir.

525
00:22:08,880 --> 00:22:09,960
Is that wise?

526
00:22:10,280 --> 00:22:11,480
Sir Yanyun was reluctant to host a banquet,

527
00:22:11,640 --> 00:22:12,200
and Madam

528
00:22:12,200 --> 00:22:13,520
- suggested a modest...
- What was that?

529
00:22:19,800 --> 00:22:20,960
Bastard.

530
00:22:24,480 --> 00:22:25,640
Mrs. Chen invited

531
00:22:25,880 --> 00:22:27,680
Jinzhao and me over,

532
00:22:27,920 --> 00:22:30,120
saying the chrysanthemums at hers are in full bloom.

533
00:22:32,120 --> 00:22:33,480
In my sickly state,

534
00:22:33,480 --> 00:22:34,960
I'd only be an unwelcome sight.

535
00:22:35,880 --> 00:22:37,000
I suspect

536
00:22:37,000 --> 00:22:38,600
Jinzhao isn't keen either.

537
00:22:39,760 --> 00:22:40,720
Let's just decline.

538
00:22:42,720 --> 00:22:43,760
Do you have any idea

539
00:22:44,480 --> 00:22:46,080
how many people in the court

540
00:22:46,240 --> 00:22:48,000
would kill to receive

541
00:22:48,000 --> 00:22:49,760
an invitation from the Chen family

542
00:22:49,760 --> 00:22:52,800
to become a guest at Chen Yanyun's table?

543
00:22:53,720 --> 00:22:56,120
They all say the Lord Chief Councilor is insinuating

544
00:22:56,120 --> 00:22:58,320
Lord Chen into the cabinet sooner or later.

545
00:22:59,200 --> 00:23:00,320
At his age?

546
00:23:00,720 --> 00:23:02,480
A cabinet minister?

547
00:23:04,080 --> 00:23:06,000
Just think how my mother-in-law

548
00:23:06,400 --> 00:23:08,400
got into Lord Chen's favor from the start.

549
00:23:08,920 --> 00:23:10,440
Such a merchant's trick.

550
00:23:10,440 --> 00:23:12,760
Prying open doors and connections with coins.

551
00:23:13,520 --> 00:23:16,600
I could never pull it off.

552
00:23:17,000 --> 00:23:18,760
Ministry of Revenue wouldn't have set eyes on you

553
00:23:19,600 --> 00:23:21,240
if not for your mother.

554
00:23:22,080 --> 00:23:23,640
That's why I say she commands my respect.

555
00:23:27,200 --> 00:23:28,760
Why hasn't Jinzhao come to eat?

556
00:23:29,640 --> 00:23:31,320
She's growing more and more unruly.

557
00:23:33,280 --> 00:23:33,920
The Chen manor

558
00:23:33,920 --> 00:23:35,440
is a most lofty household.

559
00:23:35,800 --> 00:23:36,880
Why let such a rare opportunity

560
00:23:37,640 --> 00:23:39,480
go down the drain?

561
00:23:41,960 --> 00:23:43,480
If only Rong were here.

562
00:23:44,120 --> 00:23:45,680
He could accompany his sister.

563
00:23:48,280 --> 00:23:49,200
In that case,

564
00:23:50,080 --> 00:23:51,040
Lan

565
00:23:51,400 --> 00:23:53,200
can also accompany her sister.

566
00:23:56,320 --> 00:23:57,000
Fine.

567
00:23:58,200 --> 00:23:59,520
Lan can go, then.

568
00:24:00,280 --> 00:24:01,040
The two of them

569
00:24:01,040 --> 00:24:02,400
can keep each other company.

570
00:24:05,800 --> 00:24:07,120
Why do you have to

571
00:24:07,120 --> 00:24:08,000
put on that sulky face?

572
00:24:08,200 --> 00:24:09,360
Your coming-of-age is near.

573
00:24:09,560 --> 00:24:11,080
Now is the time to get out and be seen.

574
00:24:11,480 --> 00:24:12,680
And the Chen family?

575
00:24:12,920 --> 00:24:14,200
They only associate with people of substance.

576
00:24:14,800 --> 00:24:15,560
Their fourth

577
00:24:15,560 --> 00:24:16,680
may be claimed,

578
00:24:17,080 --> 00:24:18,560
but that top scholar isn't!

579
00:24:19,400 --> 00:24:20,320
At this feast,

580
00:24:20,600 --> 00:24:22,400
there's got to be plenty of young gentlemen.

581
00:24:22,920 --> 00:24:24,200
A perfect chance to

582
00:24:24,920 --> 00:24:26,200
see and to be seen.

583
00:24:27,400 --> 00:24:28,880
What are you talking about?

584
00:24:29,160 --> 00:24:30,680
All this looking and being looked at.

585
00:24:39,720 --> 00:24:41,240
You can't embroider the wings like that.

586
00:24:51,720 --> 00:24:52,920
Didn't you ask me the other day

587
00:24:53,280 --> 00:24:54,400
why they took away that

588
00:24:54,400 --> 00:24:56,200
ebony Taiyin zither of yours?

589
00:24:56,680 --> 00:24:57,680
It's because that zither

590
00:24:57,680 --> 00:24:58,840
was part of the Madam's dowry.

591
00:24:59,600 --> 00:25:00,040
See?

592
00:25:00,840 --> 00:25:02,040
I've only just stepped down,

593
00:25:02,200 --> 00:25:03,280
and already you're targeted.

594
00:25:04,840 --> 00:25:06,440
I must have been blind back then,

595
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:08,400
to insist on marrying down,

596
00:25:09,080 --> 00:25:10,320
making you,

597
00:25:10,320 --> 00:25:11,280
my poor sweetheart,

598
00:25:11,600 --> 00:25:12,760
second-class in every way.

599
00:25:16,800 --> 00:25:18,280
Now I've come to see the truth.

600
00:25:19,280 --> 00:25:21,280
For me, this life is as good as it gets.

601
00:25:22,240 --> 00:25:23,600
But you still have a chance.

602
00:25:24,400 --> 00:25:25,880
The Chens may hold a superior rank,

603
00:25:26,320 --> 00:25:27,240
but that prize scholar...

604
00:25:27,240 --> 00:25:28,360
he was taken in from the outside.

605
00:25:28,760 --> 00:25:30,160
Not being the heiress, you're still

606
00:25:30,160 --> 00:25:31,040
more than a match for him.

607
00:25:32,080 --> 00:25:33,080
If you could only

608
00:25:33,080 --> 00:25:34,680
secure him as your husband,

609
00:25:35,560 --> 00:25:37,160
I could go to my grave in peace.

610
00:25:38,560 --> 00:25:39,440
Oh, Mother...

611
00:25:39,920 --> 00:25:41,160
Never mind whether he

612
00:25:41,160 --> 00:25:42,440
finds me to his liking.

613
00:25:42,760 --> 00:25:44,160
He might not necessarily

614
00:25:44,320 --> 00:25:45,920
