I never said I had a preference for anyone.

620
00:26:27,520 --> 00:26:35,040
His Highness the Crown Prince!

621
00:26:35,040 --> 00:26:35,840
Greetings, Your Highness.

622
00:26:36,720 --> 00:26:37,200
Sit, sit.

623
00:26:40,400 --> 00:26:41,600
You're back at last.

624
00:26:42,120 --> 00:26:42,920
Tomorrow,

625
00:26:43,320 --> 00:26:44,960
Mr. Wang is off, no lectures today.

626
00:26:45,360 --> 00:26:46,160
Tell me,

627
00:26:46,480 --> 00:26:48,160
