628
00:26:54,560 --> 00:26:55,480
What's on your mind?

629
00:26:55,880 --> 00:26:56,680
Anywhere, if

630
00:26:56,680 --> 00:26:57,520
outside these walls,

631
00:26:57,920 --> 00:26:59,200
Oh, no, no!

632
00:26:59,440 --> 00:27:00,520
Have you forgotten, Your Highness?

633
00:27:00,880 --> 00:27:02,600
Last month when we ventured out,

634
00:27:02,880 --> 00:27:03,800
it was less than a quarter

635
00:27:03,800 --> 00:27:05,320
before Lord Chen found out.

636
00:27:05,840 --> 00:27:08,000
We all took a thrashing for it.

637
00:27:08,280 --> 00:27:10,920
I still ache just thinking about it.

638
00:27:11,480 --> 00:27:12,440
Then, we'll go somewhere

639
00:27:12,440 --> 00:27:13,360
where he

640
00:27:13,360 --> 00:27:14,080
won't find us.

641
00:27:14,360 --> 00:27:15,200
Your Highness,

642
00:27:15,480 --> 00:27:17,080
I hate to be a spoilsport,

643
00:27:17,280 --> 00:27:19,000
but your safety is paramount.

644
00:27:19,080 --> 00:27:20,920
If anything were to go wrong

645
