654
00:27:40,530 --> 00:27:42,040
Peace, Your Highness.

655
00:27:42,040 --> 00:27:42,640
Think about it:

656
00:27:42,800 --> 00:27:44,000
Lord Chen is your tutor.

657
00:27:44,240 --> 00:27:45,360
What could be more natural

658
00:27:45,360 --> 00:27:46,480
