He might even have to cover for you!

665
00:27:56,280 --> 00:27:56,880
You're right!

666
00:27:57,760 --> 00:27:58,720
This would really

667
00:27:58,720 --> 00:27:59,760
back him into a corner.

668
00:28:01,560 --> 00:28:03,200
It's settled. To the Chen estate we go!

669
00:28:08,680 --> 00:28:10,040
When the former Lord Chief Councilor, Song Chong,

670
00:28:10,520 --> 00:28:11,840
