716
00:30:14,320 --> 00:30:15,360
No formalities.

717
00:30:16,400 --> 00:30:17,720
Come back here when the banquet begins.

718
00:30:18,520 --> 00:30:18,960
Yes, Ma'am.

719
00:30:19,040 --> 00:30:19,560
Yes, Ma'am.

720
00:30:20,920 --> 00:30:21,800
Let's go.

721
00:30:29,120 --> 00:30:29,960
