tried to speak up,

748
00:31:18,400 --> 00:31:19,680
and was thrashed to death.

749
00:31:22,640 --> 00:31:23,720
Bring him here right now.

750
00:31:32,120 --> 00:31:33,000
Death by suffocation.

751
00:31:33,160 --> 00:31:34,000
Mud under his fingernails.

752
00:31:34,120 --> 00:31:35,360
Must've struggled to reach the shore.

753
00:31:37,360 --> 00:31:38,280
"Yuzhu felt it improper,

754
00:31:38,480 --> 00:31:39,440
tried to speak up,

755
00:31:39,960 --> 00:31:41,280
and was thrashed to death."

756
00:31:52,880 --> 00:31:53,760
I had intended to

757
00:31:54,200 --> 00:31:55,640
deal with you after the

758
00:31:55,640 --> 00:31:56,440
