802
00:33:11,960 --> 00:33:12,440
No.

803
00:33:14,760 --> 00:33:15,600
Brother.

804
00:33:16,720 --> 00:33:17,280
Brother.

805
00:33:18,280 --> 00:33:18,840
Brother.

806
00:33:19,800 --> 00:33:20,640
Brother, I was wrong.

807
00:33:21,280 --> 00:33:21,880
Don't let her

808
00:33:21,880 --> 00:33:22,800
