809
00:33:23,920 --> 00:33:24,400
Brother.

810
00:33:24,640 --> 00:33:25,360
I swear I'll change.

811
00:33:25,360 --> 00:33:26,040
I know I was wrong.

812
00:33:26,040 --> 00:33:27,080
We are family, aren't we?

813
00:33:27,080 --> 00:33:28,320
And Fifth brother was my family too!

814
00:33:28,600 --> 00:33:30,160
He was a concubine's, way below us.

815
00:33:34,160 --> 00:33:35,000
Brother.

816
00:33:37,240 --> 00:33:38,880
You're truly set on this path, aren't you?

817
00:33:41,680 --> 00:33:43,320
How can you do this to me?

818
00:33:43,920 --> 00:33:44,400
Yes.

819
00:33:44,520 --> 00:33:45,440
I killed him.

820
00:33:45,440 --> 00:33:46,120
