00:35:58,560 --> 00:35:59,760
I'm afraid I'll have to throw

874
00:36:00,000 --> 00:36:01,280
this place into turmoil...

875
00:36:04,040 --> 00:36:05,000
Were these words

876
00:36:05,600 --> 00:36:07,200
taught to you by this cousin of yours?

877
00:36:08,360 --> 00:36:09,560
My cousin is gifted and clever.

878
00:36:09,800 --> 00:36:10,800
Of course he's self-taught.

879
00:36:11,120 --> 00:36:11,880
Indeed.

880
00:36:12,520 --> 00:36:13,680
Very well said.

881
00:36:14,080 --> 00:36:15,880
Then, at the Royal Lectures the day after tomorrow,

882
00:36:16,880 --> 00:36:18,600
you can say it all again to the Lord Chief Chancellor.

883
00:36:19,920 --> 00:36:21,760
Sir, please.

884
00:36:22,120 --> 00:36:23,720
I've only just managed to get out.

885
00:36:29,400 --> 00:36:30,880
Go fetch Xuanqing.

886
00:36:31,280 --> 00:36:32,840
He can keep Lord Ye and...

887
00:36:33,200 --> 00:36:34,480
Wang by surname. Wang Zhang.

888
00:36:34,680 --> 00:36:35,920
I'm Ye Xian's cousin.

889
00:36:37,160 --> 00:36:37,880
Good.

890
00:36:37,960 --> 00:36:40,920
Ask Xuanqing to keep Lord Ye and Mr. Wang company

891
00:36:41,400 --> 00:36:42,320
Wonderful.

892
00:36:43,320 --> 00:36:44,560
We are in your debt, Lord Chen.

893
00:36:45,200 --> 00:36:46,000
It's my duty.

894
00:36:46,920 --> 00:36:48,280
I must ask Lord Ye

895
00:36:48,720 --> 00:36:49,840
to watch carefully over

896
00:36:50,040 --> 00:36:50,800
Mr. Wang.

897
00:36:51,600 --> 00:36:52,120
Mark this:

898
00:36:52,680 --> 00:36:54,000
Do not let your guard down for a sec.

899
00:36:55,120 --> 00:36:55,920
Of course.

900
00:36:56,320 --> 00:36:57,520
Lord Chen, rest assured.

901
00:37:05,880 --> 00:37:06,640
We've only had

902
00:37:06,840 --> 00:37:07,840
close friends

903
00:37:07,840 --> 00:37:08,720
and relatives over.

904
00:37:11,400 --> 00:37:12,560
Gu Jinzhao?

905
00:37:13,760 --> 00:37:14,320
Oh, right.

906
00:37:14,520 --> 00:37:15,240
I almost forgot.

907
00:37:15,640 --> 00:37:16,920
Lord Ye and Miss Gu

908
00:37:17,160 --> 00:37:18,000
were acquainted.

909
00:37:21,680 --> 00:37:23,200
More than just acquainted, I'd say.

910
00:37:25,840 --> 00:37:26,640
This way, please.

911
00:37:34,880 --> 00:37:36,280
Xian!

912
00:37:36,880 --> 00:37:38,080
What brings you here too?

913
00:37:40,640 --> 00:37:42,040
This is my cousin, Wang Zhang.

914
00:37:43,160 --> 00:37:44,480
Already on first name terms.

915
00:37:44,880 --> 00:37:45,960
Now the curtsy's gone too?

916
00:37:46,920 --> 00:37:50,040
Greetings, Lord Ye. Greetings, Mr. Wang.

917
00:37:52,520 --> 00:37:53,360
What's this?

918
00:37:53,720 --> 00:37:54,720
Let's play together.

919
00:37:55,160 --> 00:37:56,000
Alright, alright.

920
00:37:56,440 --> 00:37:57,360
Let's play.

921
00:37:57,600 --> 00:37:58,560
Xian,

922
00:37:59,600 --> 00:38:00,640
what would you like to play?

923
00:38:02,240 --> 00:38:03,280
Anything.

924
00:38:04,040 --> 00:38:05,400
But with winners and losers.

925
00:38:05,680 --> 00:38:06,440
It's all about the thrill.

926
00:38:07,840 --> 00:38:08,840
I have an idea.

927
00:38:09,200 --> 00:38:11,080
Riddles?

928
00:38:11,640 --> 00:38:13,240
We each come up with one riddle,

929
00:38:13,360 --> 00:38:14,840
and put up a prize as stakes.

930
00:38:15,120 --> 00:38:16,000
Whoever guesses it...

931
00:38:16,000 --> 00:38:16,720
"I bet on Lord Ye."

932
00:38:16,720 --> 00:38:17,920
...wins the other's prize.

933
00:38:18,280 --> 00:38:19,280
"I follow."

934
00:38:19,680 --> 00:38:20,440
I just know

935
00:38:20,440 --> 00:38:21,160
Xian

936
00:38:21,160 --> 00:38:22,480
will take first place.

937
00:38:22,600 --> 00:38:23,640
You're right.

938
00:38:23,640 --> 00:38:24,640
Let's wait and see.

939
00:38:30,400 --> 00:38:31,200
You just can't stop

940
00:38:31,200 --> 00:38:32,480
flaunting your wealth, huh?

941
00:38:32,880 --> 00:38:34,520
A willow-leaf vase for a game?

942
00:38:35,680 --> 00:38:37,040
It's not even an antique.

943
00:38:37,320 --> 00:38:38,240
Besides,

944
00:38:38,440 --> 00:38:39,960
I couldn't think of anything else.

945
00:38:48,800 --> 00:38:50,120
A Lumi musket.

946
00:38:54,760 --> 00:38:55,360
This...

947
00:38:57,000 --> 00:38:57,880
Xian,

948
00:38:58,120 --> 00:38:58,840
how come you

949
00:38:58,840 --> 00:39:00,360
carry a weapon on your person?

950
00:39:00,880 --> 00:39:01,960
It's rather frightening.

951
00:39:01,960 --> 00:39:02,880
Frightening?

952
00:39:03,920 --> 00:39:05,200
Isn't being out and about weapon-free

953
00:39:05,640 --> 00:39:06,440
even more so?

954
00:39:16,760 --> 00:39:17,680
What are you doing?

955
00:39:17,920 --> 00:39:18,840
Are you alright?

956
00:39:21,080 --> 00:39:21,880
Lord Ye.

957
00:39:22,760 --> 00:39:23,680
That musket...

958
00:39:24,040 --> 00:39:25,400
Better not point it at people.

959
00:39:25,920 --> 00:39:26,720
What's there to fear?

960
00:39:27,080 --> 00:39:29,080
This musket isn't even loaded.

961
00:39:29,600 --> 00:39:30,560
But once you make

962
00:39:30,960 --> 00:39:32,200
a habit of fiddling with it,

963
00:39:32,640 --> 00:39:33,720
sooner or later,

964
00:39:34,200 --> 00:39:35,280
it would lead to

965
00:39:35,600 --> 00:39:36,720
some serious trouble.

966
00:39:42,440 --> 00:39:44,120
Who are you to lecture me?

967
00:39:52,120 --> 00:39:53,080
Lord Ye.

968
00:39:53,400 --> 00:39:54,040
What?

969
00:39:54,600 --> 00:39:55,680
You hear me out.

970
00:40:05,000 --> 00:40:05,680
Wanxue.

971
00:40:08,760 --> 00:40:09,800
Are you alright?

972
00:40:12,320 --> 00:40:13,640
We were just having fun.

973
00:40:13,920 --> 00:40:14,800
Can you just grow up?

974
00:40:15,880 --> 00:40:17,240
Then why are you siding with Chen Xuanqing?

975
00:40:18,720 --> 00:40:20,240
Funny. Did I?

976
00:40:21,360 --> 00:40:22,360
Today's hostess

977
00:40:22,360 --> 00:40:23,640
is Mrs. Chen.

978
00:40:24,160 --> 00:40:25,400
Go ahead and have issues

979
00:40:25,400 --> 00:40:26,360
with Chen Xuanqing.

980
00:40:26,720 --> 00:40:27,280
But you're now

981
00:40:27,280 --> 00:40:28,400
rubbing Mrs. Chen in the face.

982
00:40:30,640 --> 00:40:31,960
You do have a point there.

983
00:40:32,760 --> 00:40:33,840
I'll let him off this once.

984
00:40:36,360 --> 00:40:37,120
Are you afraid?

985
00:40:37,640 --> 00:40:38,480
Of what?

986
00:40:43,840 --> 00:40:44,880
Of dying.

987
00:40:51,080 --> 00:40:52,560
Who's really afraid of dying here?

988
00:40:53,000 --> 00:40:53,960
Someone who's never at ease,

989
00:40:54,160 --> 00:40:55,040
pulling out a dagger one moment,

990
00:40:55,040 --> 00:40:56,040
and a musket the next.

991
00:40:56,840 --> 00:40:58,240
Isn't that the definition of cowardice?

992
00:41:00,920 --> 00:41:01,680
Miss.

993
00:41:04,920 --> 00:41:06,680
The definition of cowardice...

994
00:41:10,480 --> 00:41:11,120
Baoling.

995
00:41:18,160 --> 00:41:18,760
Sir.

996
00:41:29,080 --> 00:41:29,880
Everyone's been notified.

997
00:41:30,480 --> 00:41:31,400
The Criminal Investigation Bureau

998
00:41:31,400 --> 00:41:32,800
has sent additional men.

999
00:41:33,120 --> 00:41:34,680
We've also set up covert defenses.

1000
00:41:35,480 --> 00:41:36,920
With the Crown Prince outside the palace,

1001
00:41:37,200 --> 00:41:38,440
won't it alert our enemies

1002
00:41:38,560 --> 00:41:39,600
and ruin our plan?

1003
00:41:39,960 --> 00:41:40,960
His Majesty is gravely ill,

1004
00:41:41,280 --> 00:41:42,960
and Prince Glorian is getting restless.

1005
00:41:43,400 --> 00:41:44,880
Didn't we set this trap precisely to

1006
00:41:45,360 --> 00:41:47,040
draw the snake out of its hole?

1007
00:41:48,400 --> 00:41:49,640
On the contrary, I feel

1008
00:41:50,040 --> 00:41:51,560
the Crown Prince's visit this time

1009
00:41:52,000 --> 00:41:53,120
makes our plan

1010
00:41:53,600 --> 00:41:55,040
all the more credible.

1011
00:41:56,480 --> 00:41:57,000
Sir.

1012
00:41:57,280 --> 00:41:58,440
Baoling here with something

1013
00:41:58,440 --> 00:41:59,160
to report.

1014
00:42:00,000 --> 00:42:00,680
What is it?

1015
00:42:01,520 --> 00:42:02,400
Sir.

1016
00:42:02,640 --> 00:42:04,080
Miss and the other young ladies and gentlemen

1017
00:42:04,080 --> 00:42:04,880
are playing riddles.

1018
00:42:05,160 --> 00:42:06,840
Miss Gu Jinzhao and Lord Ye

1019
00:42:06,840 --> 00:42:08,800
have put up precious prizes.

1020
00:42:09,640 --> 00:42:10,680
Miss says Sir Xuanqing

1021
00:42:11,000 --> 00:42:11,760
has never been one

1022
00:42:11,760 --> 00:42:12,800
for such amusements.

1023
00:42:13,160 --> 00:42:14,080
Worried he'll be put in a spot,

1024
00:42:14,400 --> 00:42:16,480
she'd like to ask you for something.

1025
00:42:17,400 --> 00:42:18,280
What did they put up?

1026
00:42:18,960 --> 00:42:19,840
Lord Ye

1027
00:42:20,120 --> 00:42:21,400
brought out a Lumi musket.

1028
00:42:21,880 --> 00:42:22,520
Miss Gu

1029
00:42:22,520 --> 00:42:24,280
offered a willow-leaf vase.

1030
00:42:24,720 --> 00:42:27,280
She says it's worth a hundred taels.

1031
00:42:30,400 --> 00:42:31,600
This Lord Ye

1032
00:42:31,760 --> 00:42:32,760
is a real dandy.

1033
00:42:33,080 --> 00:42:33,920
And Miss Gu?

1034
00:42:34,040 --> 00:42:35,440
She's flush with money too.

1035
00:42:37,080 --> 00:42:38,320
Lord Ye is no surprise.

1036
00:42:38,320 --> 00:42:39,320
He's always like this.

1037
00:42:40,400 --> 00:42:41,880
But Miss Gu is probably

1038
00:42:42,280 --> 00:42:44,120
leveraging this chance to

1039
00:42:44,480 --> 00:42:45,640
cozy up to us again.

1040
00:43:00,600 --> 00:43:01,600
Take this.

1041
00:43:02,360 --> 00:43:03,320
Give it to Xuanqing.

1042
00:43:04,000 --> 00:43:04,640
Yes, Sir.

1043
00:43:17,120 --> 00:43:17,840
Xuanqing.

1044
00:43:23,560 --> 00:43:24,600
"Pure and innocent."

1045
00:43:25,640 --> 00:43:27,200
Sister, what does it mean?
